title: Top gear quotes
description:
This is a small collection of quotes from the motoring show Top Gear, coded in mp3 format.
It includes Jeremy Clarkson saying &#039;How hard can it be?&#039; and James May saying &#039;Hello&#039; to a small boat he collides with, saying &#039;I love you&#039; to a french woman, saying &#039;Oh, cock!&#039; and asking about its Norwegian translation, stating his view on procedures and accusing his co-presenters of being both utter pirates and a pair of useless scurvy dogs.
Enjoy.
